30:01.292 --> 30:04.292
But Christ is compassionate, he forgives

30:04.292 --> 30:08.459
because he believes that there could be a transformation.

30:08.459 --> 30:15.417
At the level of Sri Ganesha he thinks is better

30:15.417 --> 30:19.209
that let them be killed and be born again

30:19.209 --> 30:23.459
because they're so impure but Christ had hopes

30:23.501 --> 30:25.626
that he can transform people,

30:25.626 --> 30:30.376
but he could not, they crucified him.

30:30.417 --> 30:35.793
What wonderful people they must have been to crucify Christ.

30:35.793 --> 30:41.209
Brainless we should call them, absolutely

30:41.250 --> 30:46.167
without any understanding about spirituality,

30:46.209 --> 30:51.958
very insensitive to true knowledge.

30:51.958 --> 31:00.417
So for Sahaja Yoga, only the wise can follow.

31:00.459 --> 31:07.167
It is not meant for stupid idiotic people nor it is meant for very smart ones.

31:07.209 --> 31:13.542
Some people think they are very smart because they are successful in life,

31:13.584 --> 31:17.751
they can say some smart sentences, they can say something very,

31:17.793 --> 31:23.668
outstandingly very sharp, it's not meant for that.

31:23.709 --> 31:30.042
For that Christ has said meek in heart will inherit the earth.

31:30.042 --> 31:36.876
Meek in heart, not those who think too much of themselves

31:36.876 --> 31:42.793
but for meek in heart will inherit the earth.

31:42.793 --> 31:45.751
Among Sahaja Yogis also only those who are meek in heart

31:45.793 --> 31:52.668
will inherit the blessing of Mother. You have to be meek,

31:52.709 --> 31:58.417
you have to be wise and with wisdom you'll become meek

31:58.417 --> 32:00.125
because then you will see

32:00.125 --> 32:03.459
where are we into this great cosmos,

32:03.459 --> 32:10.334
that, you will feel that you have entered into this Kingdom of God,

32:10.376 --> 32:15.958
for what? How? How have we come here?

32:15.959 --> 32:20.709
How have you entered here? So many tried,

32:20.709 --> 32:25.459
thousands of years sacrificing this sacrificing that,

32:25.501 --> 32:28.626
standing on their heads, fasting,

32:28.626 --> 32:31.626
how is it suddenly we got this blessing?

32:31.626 --> 32:33.876
How are we there?

32:33.918 --> 32:39.417
When we start looking at this we become meek.

32:39.417 --> 32:42.918
Is the blessing, is the grace.

32:42.918 --> 32:45.417
It's not through our ego,

32:45.459 --> 32:48.793
through our conditionings but is just the grace,

32:48.834 --> 32:53.125
the compassion, the love the Sandrakaruna,

32:53.125 --> 33:01.250
and then you enjoy your transformed life,

33:01.292 --> 33:09.417
the new dimension of spirituality which is in reality.

33:09.417 --> 33:12.958
Now you know reality, you know totality, you know everything

33:12.959 --> 33:16.459
but those who have not known themselves

33:16.501 --> 33:19.000
have not become Sahaja Yogis.

33:19.042 --> 33:25.793
Tukarama has said in very simple words .............

33:25.834 --> 33:31.709
the one who has known himself is the last one.

33:31.709 --> 33:36.042
You can judge the chakras of others

33:36.084 --> 33:38.167
but you can't judge your own chakras,

33:38.209 --> 33:40.501
you can introspect others,

33:40.501 --> 33:42.584
you can judge others but you cannot judge yourself.

33:42.584 --> 33:45.584
You know everything about others but about yourself

33:45.584 --> 33:50.918
you don't know anything, then you are not Sahaja Yogis.

33:50.918 --> 33:52.751
First thing you must know yourself.

33:52.751 --> 33:55.834
What sort of an ego stuff I am doing.

33:55.834 --> 33:58.250
What sort of a conditioning I have got.

33:58.250 --> 34:01.918
Even now people have so many conditionings.

34:01.958 --> 34:05.250
So there's a new discipline of Sahaja Yoga,

34:05.292 --> 34:13.876
in the new discipline you have to be meek, humble and you have to be wise.

34:13.918 --> 34:18.000
Every step of yours, every talk of yours,

34:18.042 --> 34:22.376
everything should express wisdom

34:22.417 --> 34:26.292
and the Sahaj discipline which automatically stops you

34:26.334 --> 34:28.000
from doing wrong things.

34:28.000 --> 34:30.709
Now say I'm walking down and some lady suddenly

34:30.751 --> 34:35.000
falls at my feet without even understanding that I am just walking,

34:35.000 --> 34:39.584
I may fall down or catches hold of my feet,

34:39.626 --> 34:43.709
is all self oriented.

34:43.751 --> 34:48.167
I should see Mother, I should go and meet her,

34:48.167 --> 34:51.834
I touched her feet, is all ego.

34:51.876 --> 34:57.042
A Sahaja Yogi stands in the back,

34:57.084 --> 35:05.834
real Sahaja Yogi is at the back from there he can enjoy because he knows I am everywhere.

35:05.876 --> 35:14.084
He doesn't want to see me, nothing, just like this, standing.

35:14.125 --> 35:18.834
He doesn't force his way in any way.

35:18.876 --> 35:23.000
Mother is here.

35:23.000 --> 35:29.125
But this is what it is Christ has said, meek in heart.

35:29.167 --> 35:33.084
There's a very big word "meek" and people don't understand meek

35:33.084 --> 35:36.292
because in the west if you are meek people say you are weak,

35:36.292 --> 35:38.918
you have to be aggressive. If they have to praise somebody

35:38.958 --> 35:41.584
they'll say, oh he is very good, he is very aggressive.

35:41.626 --> 35:45.876
I think their genetics are little lower than normal,

35:45.876 --> 35:51.417
must be some animals in them otherwise how can they think

35:51.417 --> 35:56.209
that to be aggressive is being something higher.

35:56.250 --> 36:04.501
It's impossible, how can a person who is supposed

36:04.542 --> 36:07.959
to be a higher person, could be like a devil.

36:08.000 --> 36:13.084
How could Hitler say that he was a higher race

36:13.125 --> 36:16.417
when he was himself a devil?

36:16.459 --> 36:20.793
Is very nice for a devil to say I am a higher race.

36:20.793 --> 36:29.376
So in dealing in Sahaja Yoga, the sweetness of natural meekness

36:29.417 --> 36:33.959
not artificial of a businessman but a natural one

36:34.000 --> 36:44.751
that makes you shine with your great, great spirituality.

36:44.793 --> 36:49.125
Nobody can touch you, I have told you, except for you.

36:49.167 --> 36:54.584
You can only fall down but nobody can touch you,

36:54.626 --> 36:57.626
you are all protected from every angle

36:57.668 --> 37:01.376
but if you want to hit yourself I can't help it.

37:01.376 --> 37:04.250
So again we come to Tukarama saying,

37:04.292 --> 37:10.209
as Christ has said "know thyself ".

37:10.209 --> 37:16.000
First and foremost thing of introspectionis know thyself.

37:16.042 --> 37:22.167
What you are doing,

37:22.209 --> 37:26.209
are you trying to look at yourself or not?

37:26.209 --> 37:34.626
He has also said that we see a big beam into the eyes of others,

37:34.668 --> 37:41.751
then it's all right, but the beam is in your eyes

37:41.793 --> 37:44.918
and you start seeing the beam in others eyes and that's.

37:44.958 --> 37:52.084
So in your meditation you have to sit down

37:52.125 --> 37:55.376
and first of all introspect-Oh Christ,

37:55.376 --> 37:59.918
Oh Sri Ganesha please give me wisdom to see myself

37:59.958 --> 38:06.834
and understand what's wrong with me and understand

38:06.876 --> 38:14.376
where do I lack all the qualities of a good Sahaja Yogi.

38:14.417 --> 38:21.958
Just to meditate and you feel so happy, so joyous,

38:21.959 --> 38:26.958
because virtue within you gives you joy.

38:27.000 --> 38:29.209
But you don't say I'm virtuous,

38:29.250 --> 38:32.459
you don't say that, but the virtue within you

38:32.501 --> 38:35.334
when you discover, that gives you joy

38:35.334 --> 38:42.292
and not your bad qualities and your hankerings,

38:42.334 --> 38:45.958
your lust and greed, no it does not.

38:45.959 --> 38:53.626
So we must really concentrate, even coming to Sahaja Yoga

38:53.668 --> 38:58.751
people think how I can use it for say fame,

38:58.751 --> 39:04.626
leadership you see is another myth. Then they sometimes think

39:04.668 --> 39:08.501
why not use it for making some money some how.

39:08.501 --> 39:12.042
Some sort of a business they start.

39:12.042 --> 39:17.250
Don't do any business with Sahaja Yoga or Sahaja Yogis,

39:17.292 --> 39:20.292
I've told a hundred times, if you do it you'll be in trouble

39:20.334 --> 39:22.834
and then don't come and tell me the trouble.

39:22.834 --> 39:29.125
Sahaja Yoga is only Gods business, that's all.

39:29.125 --> 39:39.376
Everything that you are doing is for God and that's why

39:39.376 --> 39:41.542
you are doing it for your self.

39:41.542 --> 39:45.084
So introspection is very important,

39:45.084 --> 39:50.250
criticising others should be less and criticising yourself

39:50.292 --> 39:52.459
and laughing at yourself is the best.

39:52.501 --> 39:53.834
I laugh at myself many a times

39:53.876 --> 39:57.376
and say many things like that, if you have noticed,

39:57.417 --> 40:06.042
that makes life so interesting. That will kill your ego.

40:06.084 --> 40:12.250
How I am trying to assert myself and where is the meekness

40:12.250 --> 40:18.542
that Christ has talked about. It is a natural goodness within us.

40:18.584 --> 40:26.626
Once it shines and shows, you become so beautiful, so loveable.

40:26.668 --> 40:29.292
Whether you are sitting here near me or there

40:29.334 --> 40:32.292
I know who is that kind.

40:32.334 --> 40:37.958
My heart just opens for such a personality.

40:37.958 --> 40:49.292
I know who they are. But even if I know I will never tell you,

40:49.334 --> 40:53.125
it is better that you know yourself.

40:53.167 --> 40:58.417
"Know thyself" is his message,

40:58.459 --> 41:03.459
in the real way not with deception because you are deceiving yourself,

41:03.459 --> 41:10.209
whom are you deceiving, know thyself without any deception,

41:10.209 --> 41:19.501
without any lies, with full concentration,

41:19.501 --> 41:26.751
see where is your attention going, that's how you are going to rise,

41:26.793 --> 41:30.417
you are not going to rise by seeing the defects of others

41:30.417 --> 41:35.542
but you are going to rise only by seeing your own defects.

41:35.542 --> 41:38.459
Exactly this what Christ has said,

41:38.501 --> 41:42.501
I am telling you in very, very simple words.

41:42.501 --> 41:48.501
Then he has said love thy neighbour as thyself which is a very,

41:48.542 --> 41:52.958
very big thing to say. Now is only possible in Sahaja Yoga

41:52.958 --> 41:58.084
because you are collective, those who are not collective

41:58.125 --> 42:01.876
how can they love their neighbour. I mean who is the neighbour then,

42:01.918 --> 42:04.167
nobody's the neighbour, they're outsiders,

42:04.167 --> 42:07.668
but as soon as you become collective,

42:07.668 --> 42:11.918
see today there are fifty five nations, you are all so collective,

42:11.918 --> 42:15.584
so moral, so beautiful, no complications, nothing,

42:15.626 --> 42:17.958
I am so overjoyed to see that

42:17.958 --> 42:21.584
but to make it perfect we should introspect.

42:21.584 --> 42:26.958
Socially, collectively you people have improved a lot

42:26.958 --> 42:29.958
but also individually within yourself

42:29.959 --> 42:33.125
you have to improve for your own goodness.

42:33.167 --> 42:39.584
So on this great occasion, we have to celebrate

42:39.584 --> 42:45.209
because really such a great amount of work was done by Christ

42:45.250 --> 42:48.167
though neutralised by these horrible priests,

42:48.167 --> 42:51.417
which is done in every country, in every religion

42:51.417 --> 42:55.459
but now we should take a vow to save others

42:55.501 --> 43:00.292
who are taking the name of Christ and doing something

43:00.334 --> 43:05.709
just the opposite. If it could be done, if it could be achieved

43:05.751 --> 43:09.876
through your lives Christ's work has been done.

43:09.876 --> 43:17.292
You have to now express Christ through your life, this is what it is.

43:17.334 --> 43:22.876
Through your life you can express it, through the purity,

43:22.918 --> 43:26.751
through the meekness, through the compassion

43:26.751 --> 43:35.459
and the wisdom of Christ. Absolutely fearless was he

43:35.459 --> 43:38.376
and that's why you have to be fearless

43:38.376 --> 43:44.125
because you have to be only afraid of God and nobody else,

43:44.125 --> 43:47.834
that's all and if you have done nothing wrong

43:47.876 --> 43:51.459
then there's nothing to be afraid of God also because he loves you very much.

43:51.459 --> 44:01.459
So be clear cut about everything, be understanding,

44:01.501 --> 44:08.626
you are all loveable people no doubt but you should be such

44:08.626 --> 44:12.207
that you can adore yourself and love yourself

44:12.232 --> 44:14.549
because of the virtues you have.

44:14.647 --> 44:18.981
May God Bless you all.
